                      Psalm 118 contains the spiritual meanings of the Hebrew letters; each section is numbered
                      Columetric layout of text: <locus target = "#126r #126v"/> (Ps. 148)
                    </note></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from = "128r" to = "140r"/><title type = "complete" ref= "LIT1828Mahale"/>
